# Teaching: WAI Wakeup Hub Bulletin Check — Step 3a Extension

**Type:** Protocol Enhancement
**Version:** 1.0.0
**Created:** 2026-03-22
**Safe to Auto-Adopt:** true
**Affects:** Wakeup protocol Step 3a, hub signal visibility at session start
**Prerequisite:** Hub must have WAI-Hub/Signals/incoming/ directory (from skill-wai-closeout-v2 teaching)

---

