| skill-wai-closeout-v2 applied | `grep -q "Hub Signal Bulletin" WAI-Spoke/commands/wai-closeout.md && echo PASS \|\| echo FAIL` | Wakeup bulletin check finds nowhere to route signals |

**Check before applying:**
```bash
grep -q "Hub Signal Bulletin" WAI-Spoke/commands/wai-closeout.md \
  && echo "PREREQ MET — safe to apply T-06" \
  || echo "BLOCKED — apply skill-wai-closeout-v2 (T-02) first"
```

